Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:68220,71390}{\i1}Although it took them\Na long time, Isabelle and Jean
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:71390,75311}{\i1}succeeded in avoiding many dangers\Nand delivered the secret letter to London.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:75311,78856}{\i1}Despite having an arrest warrant\Nlooming over their heads,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:78856,82568}{\i1}thanks to Victor's help, they managed\Nto return to Versailles without problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:88282,93746}{\i1}At that time in Versailles,\Nas if just waiting for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93746,96874}{\i1}a rather peculiar event occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116518,118520}What a beautiful ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118520,121357}This is my first opportunity\Nto admire such a perfect gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121357,125819}Oh, please. Compared to your diamond,\Nit is but a worthless pebble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141126,142753}What happened?\NWhat happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142753,145464}Why did the lights go out?\NI do not like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148384,150302}Where's my necklace?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150302,151970}And the rings!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151970,153055}They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153347,154807}They disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154807,156558}Our jewelry is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156558,159436}What to do?\NWhere has it gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160646,164066}Honey, my…\NMy necklace…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164066,167945}Get a grip, Bridget.\NDon't panic over a handful of pearls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170906,172700}A picture of a bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175703,179873}"To the people of Versailles,\Nsetting the limits of human wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179873,184420}You have our sincere gratitude for\Nyour huge donation to our shadow army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185045,186338}– Count Red".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188090,189591}Count Red?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189591,191593}Count Red?\NIs that his doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200269,201728}Let's go.
