Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.39,0:24:58.73,ED JP,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1493394,1498732}{\blur0.5}soyokaze no you ni\Natatakai ai ga aru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.73,0:25:03.65,ED JP,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1498732,1503654}{\blur0.5}RANRARA hazunda uta wa\Nogawa wo koete
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.65,0:25:08.82,ED JP,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1503654,1508826}{\blur0.5}midori no yama ni\Nkodama suru
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.82,0:25:14.16,ED JP,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1508826,1514164}{\blur0.5}hora omoikiri\Nkakete yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.16,0:25:20.46,ED JP,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1514164,1520462}{\blur0.5}ano hito no iru\Noka no ue made
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.38,0:24:53.39,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1487388,1493394}Your smile is so nice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.39,0:24:58.73,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1493394,1498732}It displays so much love,\Ngentle like a breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.73,0:25:03.65,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1498732,1503654}La la la, our song\Nreaches across the stream
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.65,0:25:08.82,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1503654,1508826}and echoes in the green mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.82,0:25:14.16,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1508826,1514164}Let's run with all our might
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.16,0:25:20.46,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1514164,1520462}to the top of the hill,\Nwhere our friend is
